            "notes": "The deck focuses on aggressive strategies with a strong emphasis on graveyard interaction and reanimation. Celes, Rune Knight leads the charge, backed up by powerful creatures like Archon of Cruelty, Elesh Norn, and Griselbrand. The deck aims to quickly fill the graveyard with cards like Buried Alive and Faithless Looting, then bring back threats with cards like Reanimate and Unburial Rites. The deck also includes disruption in the form of Thoughtseize and Swords to Plowshares to control the opponent's board. With a mix of fast creatures, powerful reanimation spells, and disruptive elements, this deck looks to overwhelm opponents with a combination of speed and resilience."
